---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { SITE, GAME } from '../consts';
---
<Base
  title="About — A Fan Guide to Moonlight Peaks | Moonlight Peaks Wiki & Guide"
  description="About Moonlight Peaks Wiki & Guide, an independent fan-made guide and wiki for the cozy vampire life sim Moonlight Peaks."
  path="/about"
  crumbs={[{ label: 'About' }]}
>
  <article class="page">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h1>About the <em>Almanac</em></h1>
      <p class="intro">
        Moonlight Peaks Wiki &amp; Guide is a clean, fast, fan-made guide to {GAME.title} — built so players can find
        what they need without wading through clutter.
      </p>

      <h2>What we do</h2>
      <p>
        We track release info, beginner tips, the Nokturna card game, romance and the seven families,
        cheats, crops, fishing, and more. We aim to be accurate and well-sourced: where something
        isn't confirmed yet, we say so rather than guess.
      </p>

      <h2>Not official</h2>
      <p>
        Moonlight Peaks Wiki &amp; Guide is independent and not affiliated with, endorsed by, or connected to
        {GAME.developer} or {GAME.publisher}. “{GAME.title}” and all related names and assets are
        trademarks of their respective owners. If you represent the game and have a concern, contact
        us and we'll respond promptly.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Corrections, tips, or new guide requests: {SITE.contact}.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>
